Description: This package contains functions to generate and calculate the pdf, cdf and icdfs of random variables following triangular and bimodal triangular-linked random variables. These functions are used to generate random variables from the multivariate case using a Gaussian copula.
Depends: R (>= 4.0.0)
Imports: copula, stats, caret, graphics, mixtools
